Fun_cemetery_v7 public - a dark map where players are on cemetery, if any player fall down to the tomb will spawn in house as a ZOMBIE with knive and he grenade.

THIS MAP DOES NOT REQUIRE ZOMBIE MOD.

This map includes weapons:
- Shotguns M3
- Knives
- He Grenades
- Smoke Grenades

DON'T CRITIC THATS TOO DARK, ITS PROJECTED TO BE DARKED.

Thanks for playing :)
